Invocation Name: digital drawing fun facts
des:
Ask for digital drawing fun facts, and learn interesting information about digital art.

Digital Drawing Fun Facts provides fun and facts about digital art.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Digital Drawing Fun Facts" or "Alexa, open Digital Drawing Fun Facts" to get a fact.

At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
